30 SECTION 4. Arkansas Code § 23-115-103(14), concerning the definition
31 of "lottery proceeds" under the Arkansas Scholarship Lottery Act, is amended
32 to read as follows:
33 (14) “Lottery proceeds” means all revenue derived from the sale
34 of tickets or shares and all other moneys derived from or in connection with
35 the operation of a lottery, including without limitation fees, offsets,
36 reimbursements, interest, insurance proceeds, damages, and liquidated damages
