16 SECTION 11. Arkansas Code § 23-115-801(d)(1), concerning findings of
17 the General Assembly related to lottery proceeds under the Arkansas
18 Scholarship Lottery Act, is amended to read as follows:
19 (d)(1) The General Assembly finds that:
20 (A) The administration of scholarships with proceeds from
21 the lottery are expenses of the office; and
22 (B) Because because the division has the expertise and
23 experienced staff needed to efficiently and appropriately administer the
24 scholarships, the office shall use the services of the division to administer
25 scholarships funded with net proceeds from the lottery.
